1. Create new Rails 3 project
2. In Gemfile add
  gem "rails", "3.0.pre"
  gem "very_nifty_generators"

3. In console run
    $ gem bundle

Will install the very_nifty_generators gem in your rails 3 project

4. Check installation
    $ script/generate

Nifty:
  nifty:authentication
  nifty:config
  nifty:layout
  nifty:scaffold


Scaffold:
    $ script/generate nifty:scaffold post name:string

Authentication:
    $ script/generate nifty:authentication

Config:
    $ script/generate nifty:config

Layout:
    $ script/generate nifty:layout

Executables: Available anywhere without having to do gem bundle! 
  nifty_auth
  nifty_config
  nifty_layout
  nifty_scaffold [model:string] [attributes:hash]

Example  
$ nifty_scaffold Person name:string birthdate:date

    
